data.description: This is a great home for sale, offering a spacious 4 bedroom 2 bath design with a flex room, and plent of parking on a corner lot! This house offers an ideal layout for modern living, with a open concept between the kitchen, living room, and dining area to fit most hosting needs. The bedrooms are generously sized, and the flex room gives you the perfect space to add extra living space or use as a home office. This home has a detached garage, with covered storage and a storage shed. Plety of parking and a ample deck and yard for hosting activities and gatherings. This home is sure to hit with any buyer!!
